      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «اَلْوِصَالُ اَلَّذِي نُهِيَ عَنْهُ هُوَ أَنْ يَجْعَلَ اَلرَّجُلُ عَشَاءَهُ سَحُورَهُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2047 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"The continuous fasting (wisal) that is prohibited is when a person makes his evening meal (iftar) the same as his pre-dawn meal (suhoor).\""
        ]
      }
    },
